cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV

The paper presents a framework for deep reinforcement learning research, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The framework includes distributed training, which involves robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also evaluates the framework on benchmarks in continuous control, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) for processing visual inputs.
